data.description: This GORGEOUS 2 story home is located minutes away from shopping, dining, schools, water park, and the Brand New Durango Casino & Hotel. As you enter this 4 bedroom home, you are greeted by an open floor plan, hardwood flooring throughout the home. All the bedrooms are located on the second level. The backyard is very low maintenance, with room to grow your own herbs and has two trees that produce peaches and mandarins. This property also has a Reverse Osmosis system, Solar Panels (SUPER LOW ENERGY BILL- Bill Range $13-$20), and Soft Water System that are PAID OFF!!
